The '''Thrawn Simulator''' was a program developed after the defeat of [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]] to test ship [[Commander/Legends|commanders]] on their tactics against one of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] greatest military geniuses. [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Nek Bwua'tu]], a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]], was the first [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] and then [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] commander to consistently defeat the Thrawn Simulator in tests.

